    • Method Detail

      • build

        WritableProperty<?> build(com.orientechnologies.orient.core.metadata.schema.OProperty oProperty,
                          OrientBean prototype)
        Ensures that the given OProperty is available in the the given OrientBean prototype.
        Parameters:
        oProperty - the OProperty.
        prototype - the OrientBean prototype.
        Returns:
        the property corresponding to the given OProperty that has been created or was already existing. May be null if the property type is not supported (e.g. if new version of OrientDB introduces new property type that has not yet been implemented here).
        See Also:
        BeanAccess.getOrCreateProperty(String, net.sf.mmm.util.reflect.api.GenericType, Class)
